description: Removes the association between a tracker resource and a geofence collection.

parameters.name: TrackerName
parameters.description: The name of the tracker resource to be dissociated from the consumer.

parameters.name: ConsumerArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the geofence collection to be disassociated from the tracker resource. Used when you need to specify a resource across all Amazon Web Services. Format example: arn:aws:geo:region:account-id:geofence-collection/ExampleGeofenceCollectionConsumer.
